===pyimc-0.3.0 20010050X===

Bugs Fixed

Features
 + toggle Skype buddy list command

Enhancements / Tasks
 + command support
 + command 'help' to list all available commands
 + command 'openchat' for old functionality
 + command 'toggle' to toggle the im buddy list

